## Question Types

The quiz system supports multiple question types:

```jsx
// Multiple Choice Questions
<MultipleChoiceQuestion
  question={question}
  options={options}
  onAnswer={handleAnswer}
/>

// Open-Ended Questions
<OpenEndedQuestion
  question={question}
  onAnswer={handleAnswer}
/>

// Case Study Questions
<CaseStudyQuestion
  scenario={scenario}
  question={question}
  onAnswer={handleAnswer}
/>
```

## Learning Analytics

- **Quiz Results**: [QuizResults.jsx](mdc:src/components/subjects/QuizResults.jsx) - Performance tracking
- **Quiz History**: [QuizHistory.jsx](mdc:src/components/subjects/QuizHistory.jsx) - Learning progress
- **Performance Data**: Track completion rates, scores, and learning patterns

## Content Structure

- **Subjects**: Top-level learning categories
- **Lectures**: Individual lessons within subjects
- **Briefs**: AI-generated summaries of lecture content
- **Quizzes**: Assessments based on lecture material
- **Flashcards**: Spaced repetition study aids

## AI Integration Guidelines

- Use loading states during AI content generation
- Implement error handling for AI service failures
- Provide fallback content when AI generation fails
- Show progress indicators for long-running operations
- Cache generated content to avoid regeneration
